description: Deletes a delegation signer (DS) record in the registry zone for this domain name.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: An internal identification number assigned to each DS record after it's created. You can retrieve it as part of DNSSEC information returned by GetDomainDetail.

nested_items.name: OperationId
nested_items.description: Identifier for tracking the progress of the request. To query the operation status, use GetOperationDetail.
